total is $562MM. CEGE market cap today is $600MM. ABGX is already down about
70% from it's high and CEGE has or is in process of getting around 500 patents
in its realm of biotech expertise. Comparable companies have marketcaps of
300-500MM without the cash and abgx shares. I think its a compelling value at
these levels, and much higher. MRVC has a subsidiary which IMHO is developing
