well informed of cutting edge developments [The comments I posted were off the
cuff not heavily researched] In the midwest, we get multiple pay-per-view
choices - 20+. With a VCR or the new TIVO recorders considering the
concentrated 'hit-oriented' nature of movies [top 20 releases at any one time
garner 90+% of demand/revenue] you have close equivalent to VOD without the
fancy infrastructure.
